<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Threads of Equality</title>

<style>

body {
font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
margin: 0;
background-color: #ffffff;
color: #333;
text-align: center;
}

/* Navigation Bar */

nav {
background-color: #111;
padding: 15px;
}

nav a {
color: white;
margin: 20px;
text-decoration: none;
font-size: 18px;
}

nav a:hover {
text-decoration: underline;
}

/* Hero Section */

.hero {
padding: 80px 20px;
background: linear-gradient(to right, #f7f7f7, #eaeaea);
}

.hero h1 {
font-size: 48px;
margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.hero p {
font-size: 20px;
}

/* Sections */

.section {
padding: 50px 20px;
max-width: 800px;
margin: auto;
}

/* Button */

.button {
display: inline-block;
margin-top: 20px;
padding: 12px 25px;
background-color: black;
color: white;
text-decoration: none;
border-radius: 5px;
}

.button:hover {
background-color: #444;
}

/* Footer */

footer {
margin-top: 40px;
padding: 20px;
background-color: #111;
color: white;
}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<nav>

<a href="#">Home</a>

<a href="#about">About Us</a>

<a href="https://instagram.com/YOURUSERNAME" target="_blank">
Instagram
</a>

</nav>


<section class="hero">

<h1>Threads of Equality</h1>

<p>Standing together against discrimination</p>

<a href="#about" class="button">Learn More</a>

</section>


<section id="about" class="section">

<h2>About Us</h2>

<p>

Threads of Equality is a student-led social project dedicated to promoting equality and preventing discrimination.

We believe that every person deserves respect regardless of religion, gender, culture, or background.

Through awareness, creativity, and community action, we aim to make our school and society a more inclusive place.

</p>

</section>


<footer>

© 2026 Threads of Equality

</footer>

</body>

</html>
